flowchart TD
    subgraph Client[Presentation Layer - React + TypeScript]
        C1[Candidate Assessment UI]
        C2[Recruiter Monitoring Dashboard]
        C3[Administrator Console]
    end

    subgraph App[Application Layer - Flask REST API]
        A1[Authentication & RBAC / MFA]
        A2[Assessment & Session Orchestration]
        A3[Risk-Scoring Engine]
        A4[Notification Service]
        A5[Audit & Reporting]
    end

    subgraph AI[AI Monitoring Layer]
        M1[Face Recognition]
        M2[Object Detection]
        M3[Eye-Gaze Tracking]
        M4[Head-Pose Estimation]
        M5[Browser-Activity Monitor]
    end

    subgraph Data[Data Layer - PostgreSQL]
        D1[(Users & Profiles)]
        D2[(Assessments & Questions)]
        D3[(Sessions & Answers)]
        D4[(Integrity Events & Evidence)]
        D5[(Notifications & Audit Logs)]
    end

    subgraph Ext[Integration Layer]
        E1[Email Gateway / SMTP]
        E2[SMS Gateway / Africa's Talking]
    end

    Client -->|HTTPS / REST| App
    Client -->|Webcam & browser events| AI
    AI -->|Integrity events| App
    App --> Data
    A3 --> A4
    A4 --> Ext
